languages.text: Путь Владайма Токара обрывается в рядах штрафной абордажной группы на корабле Инцендии Чорда. Утверждали, что он погиб при подавлении планетарного бунта, обернув оружие против товарищей.
Vladaym Tocara's path comes to an end in the ranks of the penal boarding team on Incendia Chorda's ship. People say he died putting down a planetary rebellion, turning his weapon on his comrades.

languages.text: 弗拉迪姆·托卡拉的人生道路在因森蒂娅·库尔达的船上迎来了终点。人们都说他是在镇压行星叛乱的过程中丧了命，因为他用武器指着他的战友。
languages.original_text: Vladaym Tocara's path comes to an end in the ranks of the penal boarding team on Incendia Chorda's ship. People say he died putting down a planetary rebellion, turning his weapon on his comrades.

traits.locale_text: 弗拉迪姆·托卡拉的人生道路在因森蒂娅·库尔达的船上迎来了终点。人们都说他是在镇压行星叛乱的过程中丧了命，因为他用武器指着他的队友。

languages.text: Vladaym Tocaras Pfad endet in den Reihen des Straftrupps auf Incendia Chordas Schiff. Es heißt, er sei bei der Niederschlagung einer planetaren Rebellion gestorben, als er seine Waffen auf seine Kameraden gerichtet hat.

traits.locale_text: Vladaym Tocaras Pfad endet in den Reihen des Straftrupps auf Incendia Chordas Schiff. Es heißt, er sei bei der Niederschlagung einer planetaren Rebellion gestorben, als er seine Waffen auf seine Kameraden gerichtet hat.

languages.text: La vie de Vladaym Tocara prit fin dans les rangs de l'équipe d'abordage pénale du vaisseau d'Incendia Chorda. On raconte que c'est en tentant de mater une rébellion planétaire, qu'il trouva la mort après avoir retourné son arme contre ses camarades.
languages.original_text: Vladaym Tocara's path comes to an end in the ranks of the penal boarding team on Incendia Chorda's ship. People say he died putting down a planetary rebellion, turning his weapon on his comrades.

traits.locale_text: La vie de Vladaym Tocara prit fin dans les rangs de l'équipe d'abordage pénale du vaisseau d'Incendia Chorda. On raconte qu'il trouva la mort en retournant son arme contre ses coéquipiers pour mater une rébellion planétaire.

languages.text: El camino de Vladaym Tocara termina en las filas del equipo de abordaje penal de la nave de Incendia Chorda. La gente dice que murió poniendo fin a una rebelión planetaria, disparando a sus camaradas.
languages.original_text: Vladaym Tocara's path comes to an end in the ranks of the penal boarding team on Incendia Chorda's ship. People say he died putting down a planetary rebellion, turning his weapon on his comrades.

traits.locale_text: El camino de Vladaym Tocara termina en las filas del equipo de abordaje penal de la nave de Incendia Chorda. La gente dice que murió poniendo fin a una rebelión planetaria, disparando a sus camaradas.

languages.text: ヴラダイム・トカラの道は、インセンディア・チョーダの船の流刑搭乗チームの隊列の中で終わりを告げる。彼は惑星の反乱を鎮圧し、仲間に武器を向けて死んだと人々は言う。
languages.original_text: Vladaym Tocara's path comes to an end in the ranks of the penal boarding team on Incendia Chorda's ship. People say he died putting down a planetary rebellion, turning his weapon on his comrades.

traits.locale_text: ヴラダイム・トカラの道は、インセンディア・チョーダの船の流刑搭乗チームの隊列の中で終わりを告げる。彼は惑星の反乱を鎮圧し、仲間に武器を向けて死んだと人々は言う。

languages.text: Vladaym Tocara, yolun sonuna İncendia Chorda'nın gemisindeki cezai bir bordalama ekibinin saflarındayken geldi. Bir gezegendeki isyanı bastırırken, silahını kendi yoldaşlarına çevirdiğinde öldüğü söyleniyor.

traits.locale_text: Vladaym Tocara, yolun sonuna İncendia Chorda'nın gemisindeki cezai bir bordalama ekibinin saflarındayken geldi. Bir gezegendeki isyanı bastırırken, silahını kendi yoldaşlarına çevirdiğinde öldüğü söyleniyor.
